<item>
            <title>[SOLR-12594] MetricsHistoryHandler.getOverseerLeader fails when hostname contains hyphen</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-12594</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;as reported on the user list...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We encounter a lot of log warning entries from the MetricsHistoryHandler saying&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;o.a.s.h.a.MetricsHistoryHandler Unknown format of leader id, skipping:&lt;br/&gt;
244550997187166214-server1-b.myhost:8983_solr-n_0000000094&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t even know what this &lt;em&gt;MetricsHistoryHandler&lt;/em&gt; does, but at least there&apos;s a warning.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Looking at the code you can see that it has to fail if the hostname of the node contains a hyphen:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;[] ids = oid.split(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;-&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (ids.length != 3) { &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// unknown format
&lt;/span&gt;  log.warn(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Unknown format of leader id, skipping: &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + oid);
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;;
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
